            "body": "<p>Two populer javascript MVC frameworks:  <\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://backbonejs.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://backbonejs.org/<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"http://knockoutjs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://knockoutjs.com/<\/a>  <\/p>\n\n<p>You can try them personally. suggestion are always subjective, your choice are always subjective as well. so just feel it yourself.<\/p>\n",
